Title: Relates to the hours during which liquor and/or wine stores may be open on Sunday
Summary: Relates to the hours during which liquor and/or wine stores may be open on Sunday by allowing liquor and/or wine stores to open at 10:00 a.m. rather than noon on Sunday.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the alcoholic beverage control law, in relation to the hours during which liquor and/or wine stores may be open on Sunday
